Who?

1348
01:35:33,227 --> 01:35:34,853
The fifth element.

1349
01:35:35,146 --> 01:35:39,315
The supreme being sent to Earth
to save the universe.

1350
01:35:39,483 --> 01:35:42,110
Leeloo?
Yes.

1351
01:35:42,987 --> 01:35:46,364
But she's more fragile
than she seems.

1352
01:35:46,866 --> 01:35:48,950
She needs your help...

1353
01:35:49,660 --> 01:35:51,619
