What?

1361
01:36:19,523 --> 01:36:21,983
The stones. Where are the stones?

1362
01:36:22,151 --> 01:36:23,359
The stones.

1363
01:36:31,160 --> 01:36:33,203
[LAUGHING]

1364
01:36:34,914 --> 01:36:36,998
[CRYING]

