1366
01:36:39,835 --> 01:36:42,045
The stones, where are they?

1367
01:36:43,547 --> 01:36:45,048
In me.

1368
01:36:45,424 --> 01:36:47,300
What? What?

1369
01:36:53,557 --> 01:36:55,850
Oh, my God, Korben.
Oh, my God, Korben, Korben.
Korben, another one coming.

1370
01:36:56,018 --> 01:36:57,852
Korben. Korben,
I think we should go.

1371
01:36:58,020 --> 01:36:59,562
One minute. One minute.
Just give me a minute.

