get yourself into these positions?

1485
01:44:42,693 --> 01:44:43,985
Come on.

1486
01:44:47,197 --> 01:44:50,199
Yeah, I'm here. It's all right.
It's all right. Everything's okay now.

1487
01:44:50,659 --> 01:44:51,701
Listen.

1488
01:44:52,035 --> 01:44:54,161
[TICKING]

1489
01:44:54,329 --> 01:44:57,331
